ss contaminants are galaxy groups with masses \${\textbackslash}sim3\$-\$5{\textbackslash}times 10{\textasciicircum}\{13\} \$ M\$\_{\textbackslash}odot\$ which are beyond the sensitivity of current SZE and X-ray surveys but a natural target for SPT-3G and eROSITA.},
